productBaseInfoV1.title: EMPREUS evb10 Video Glasses(white)
productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: It is a great supplement and extending device of the network set-top box and bring you wonderful experience of watching movies and playing games. Materials: Uses ABS andF42mm spherical resin lens material without stimulation plastic sheet, environmental. Offers you super 3D picture effect and wonderful feeling. Simulating Viewing Distance: Offer you a 1000 inches big screen at the distance of 3m. Easy to put your smart phone into the 3D glasses (Easily pull the smart phone storage box out, the put your smart phone in it). Perfectly suitable your face when you wear the 3D VR GLASSES. Flexible and adjustable headband is suitable for different people. You will not feel visual fatigue and dizzy even you use it for a long time because of the resin lens. Adjustable pupil distance and sight distance, satisfying different groups of people. (Optical Axis Sliding Control function: You can slightly adjust the position of the spherical resin lens through moving the button on the top of the 3D VR GLASSES so as to get a better experience of watching movies.) Greatly enjoy a private visual feast comfortably and convenient to use, allowing you watch at anytime anywhere whether sitting, lying or standing as you like, no need any software; it is a great companion for traveling or staying house. Suitable for almost all kinds of smart phones (Android / IOS, etc) that screen between 4.7~6.0 inches. Both sides holes of the 3D VR GLASSES is specially designed for the headset / data / charge cable, letting you charge your smart phone (You had better not charge your phone during enjoying movies). With compact portable design, easy to carry.

productBaseInfoV1.title: AuraVR Official Marvel ActionHero Captain America Virtual Reality (VR Headset) Video Glasses(White/Black)
productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: Official Marvel Civil War (Captain America/Iron Man), Clash of Super Heroes Plastic 6 Inch Virtual Reality Viewer (VR Headset) from AuraVR Inspired by Google CardboardExperience virtual reality on your smart phoneFits any smart phone upto 6 inch screen sizeFull plastic body, comes with magnetic triggerAdjustable strap with vertical supportOpen side slits with anti sliding cushionContact: 0172-4681840 and support@getcardboard.inProduct DescriptionThis officially licensed Civil War theme VR viewer from AuraVR is a full plastic body virtual reality viewer inspired from Google Cardboard. It can be used with smart phones with up to 6 inch screen size with minimum operating system as Android 4.1 or Apple iOS 6. It is made from flexible plastic thus making it more durable than the cardboard made viewers. This virtual reality headset comes with an adjustable head strap which distributes the weight of headset and phone evenly over the head thus making it possible to use the headset for longer duration without any strain. It comes with a magnetic trigger which is used in certain gaming applications and application selection but for this magnetic trigger to work, phone must have a magnetometer and a gyro sensor. This virtual reality headset is used for experiencing virtual reality, enjoying 360 degree movies and playing VR games on smart phones. It works on split screen methodology. You just need to install a virtual reality application (many of them are available for free on Google play store) on your mobile phone, open the lid of the viewer, insert the mobile phone, close the lid and indulge your self into the world of Virtual Reality! Since mobile phones comes with variable sizes, it may happen that only mobile screen will be covered under display area instead of complete phone but the viewing experience won't be effected.Product InformationTechnical DetailsItem Weight159 gProduct Dimensions16 x 12 x 11 cmSpecial featuresPlastic VR headset, Supports phones up to 6 inches screen size, Open slit design with anti sliding cushion, Adjustable headstrap, Magnetic triggerWhats in the boxVirtual Reality Viewer, Head Strap, Instruction Manual

productBaseInfoV1.title: AuraVR Pro VR Headset/Virtual Reality Gear comes with 42mm lenses(Smart Glasses)
productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: AuraVR Pro VR Headset is made from finest quality plastic making it more durable and light in weight. This design is a successful result of indepth research, industry experience and customer feedbacks. It is inspired from Google Cardboard, Oculus Rift & Gear VR. It can support smart phones with varied sizes ranging from 3.5"-6" and can be used with spectacles. UNIQUE FEATURES - AuraVR Pro allows you to adjust the Inter Pupillary Distance & the distance between the lens and the screen for better focus. Both the lenses can be adjusted independently and INDIVIDUALLY which is a UNIQUE and added feature in this headset. Also it uses One Finger Phone Insertion Mechanism thus making it easier to insert your phone and thus easy immersive viewing experience. IMPROVED DESIGN & QUALITY -If your smart phone gets heated during the longer usage hours, then this VR box comes with removable front lid AND AIR VENTS for easy heat dissipation. Lenses are the most important part of the VR headset and here we are using improved nano coated optical resin 42 mm lenses and 100-110 FOV. It also comes with best in class adjustable head strap, head mount and back of head cushion support. FREEBIES - Package includes FREE AuraVR Bluetooth Gaming Remote that allows you to control & click within your VR app/game without the need of taking the phone out of the headset. The remote can additionally be used for clicking selfies. The remote has full gaming buttons & a joystick that can be used even to play VR games on your mobile. COMPATIBILITY - Mobile phones running with operating system as android 4.1 and above or iOS 5 and above. For utilizing complete functionality of VR headset, phone must have sensors like Gyro sensor,proximity sensor & magnetometer. It works with almost all the smart phones with above mentioned sensors and operating system. Some popular supported smart phone brands include - Samsung, Asus, Redmi, Xiaomi, Coolpad, Micromax, Karbonn, HTC, Motorola, LG, Apple, Lenovo etc. AuraVR Pro VR headset is brought to you by the pioneers of Virtual Reality in India. productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: Meet the sporty, waterproof WS413 all-in-one MP3 player headphones from Sony. Workout harder with these in-ear sports headphones with built-in Walkman. When the going gets tough, the NW-WS413 Sports Walkman is with you every step of the way. Built to withstand the elements, it's the ultimate training partner. You're ready to train in all weathers and any conditions - and so is the NW-WS413. The NW-WS413 is made for the elements. It's ready for the ocean with an IP65/68 waterproof rating to a depth of 2 metres. It's ready for the beach with a sealed design that protects against sand, dust and grit. And it's ready for extremes as it can handle temperatures ranging from -5C to 45C. The NW-WS413 Sports Walkman also boasts an Ambient Sound Mode which lets you hear a degree of external sound so you can talk to a friend or trainer while listening to music. Waterproof and Dustproof to IP65/IP68 specifications, the NW-WS413 Walkman will maintain operability when submerged in water to a depth of 2 M for up to 30 minutes - even in salt water. The swimming earbuds must be used for the waterproof design to function correctly. Please note, after usage in salt water always wash your Walkman according to the supplied instructions.Work out in the height of summer or the depths of winter. The NW-WS413 can handle almost any weather conditions and temperatures from -5 degrees Celsius to 45 degrees Celsius.Ambient Sound Mode uses the microphones built into the left and right side of the Walkman to allow you to hear the ambient sounds around you, even as you listen to music. So, you can listen to your fitness instructor or talk to your friends without missing a beat.From beaches to dusty mountain trails, there’s no need to worry about dirt or small particles entering the NW-WS413. It’s waterproof and dustproof to IP65/IP68 specifications, giving you complete confidence in your Walkman’s performance.This Walkman is built into a headset with an all-in-one design that lets you focus on your workout rather than a tangle of wires. An ergonomic shape around the ear ensures a secure, stable fit, even during vigorous exercise. Stay fully focused on your workout. The Walkman's superior fit lets you do a range of sports and activities in complete comfort. A wireless lightweight design for long-lasting comfort, step after step, mile after mile. Before you hit the courts or the pool, preload your favourite tracks, albums, and workout playlists onto a built-in Walkman. With 4 GB you’ll never be short of tunes, even when powering through the longest workout.Running out the door to workout? Charge the NW-WS413 Walkman for just 3 minutes and get a full 60 minutes of use. With an impressive total battery life of up to 12 hours on a full charge and ready to go.Hit the water and attach swimming earbuds. Unlike standard earbuds, a thin membrane covers each earbud to prevent water damage.Take your music to new places with the brand new wearable WS413 Walkman®. A new, tough, salt water and dust proof design allows you to enjoy more activities in a wider variety of conditions; it can accompany you on your morning swim in the pool, your evening jog along the beach or your yearly hike up a snowy mountain.Listening to music whilst exercising is a true motivator, so why not make it easier than ever? A wire-free round and seamless shape makes the fit comfortable and secure, so you don’t need to worry about the Walkman® slipping at a crucial time.The WS413 wearable Walkman® from Sony is now salt-water proof and dust proof[i] so you can listen to your favourite songs whilst enjoying water sports such as kayaking or swimming and its sleek design eliminates drag interference so you are not restricted in any way. This has been enabled by the addition of an internal terminal which resists any accumulation of foreign particles and is highly corrosion-resistant. A rustproof coating on the surface of the front case ensures that your Walkman® is protected both inside and out.The WS413 comes equipped with both everyday earbuds, and specially designed waterproof earbuds[ii] that are covered with a thin film to form a barrier against water getting through without compromising comfort.But you don’t have to be in to sports to enjoy the WS413 Walkman®. The sand tolerance means it’s great for those beach days and exotic holidays. The unique sealed structure equalizes compression ratios, ensuring that your Walkman® stays Dustproof in a variety of environments. The supported temperature feature has been extended means you can use your Walkman® to its full potential in temperatures from -5°C to 45°C.You can also remain conscious of the voices and noises around you should you so wish with the new Ambient Sound mode. In-built microphones pick up ambient sounds around you allowing you to stay in touch with your surrounding environment without having to remove the device or lower the volume.

productBaseInfoV1.title: PHILIPS HTS3532BL/94 5.1 Home Theatre System
productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: Imagine having a marathon of horror movies on Halloween or even just watching your favorite animated movie for the 100th time on an entertainment system so powerful that the media comes alive. This is where the Philips HTS3532BL/94 5.1 Home Theatre System comes into the picture to make the simple act, an experience. Design and Technology Surround sound takes new directions and proportions with this Philips HTS3532BL/94 5.1 Home Theatre System with its exposed speaker drivers that transfer the thump of the music right into your heart. The system supports CD players, DVD players, USB devices and VCD players as well, along with the ability of connecting to your television to bring alive the characters of your favorite soap opera. The Home Theatre System from Philips has a standard 5.1 speaker configuration. Speakers The HTS3532BL/94 5.1 Home Theatre System from Philips comes with one centre speaker, with a power of 50 W, and four satellite speakers, all of which have an impedance of 4 ohms and a frequency response of 150 - 20K Hz. The one passive 50 W subwoofer brings the bass alive with its 4 ohm impedance and 20 - 150 Hz frequency response. Get the party started with a total power of 300 W on this system from Philips. Playback This Home Theatre System from Philips is capable of playing a lot of media types like DVD+R/+RW, DVD-R/-RW, DVD-Video, CD, CD-R/-RW, CDDA, SVCD and VCD, compatibility issues for your old and cherished movies are now not a problem. Media that is compressed could miss out on quality but this system from Philips can play DivX Ultra, MPEG1, MPEG2, MPEG4, MP3 and WMA audio and videos. You can also view JPEG images with rotate, slideshow with music playback and zoom options for refreshing memories of happy times. Video and Audio Features The HTS3532BL/94 5.1 Home Theatre System from Philips is capable of playing 720p, 1080p and 1080i formats; you can watch all-time favorite movies like Tangled and Ratatouille with your children and watch their faces light up over the stories that come to life right in your living room. The system also boasts of progressive scanning and video upscaling where necessary to give you the best that you can get. Sound is one of the most important elements of any media and entertainment experience and this system does not disappoint with its powerful Dolby Digital surround sound system. The equalizer has five settings: gaming, movie, music, news and original enabling you to optimize audio according to what you are playing. The system comes with a night mode, MP3 player support and an audio return channel apart from realistic audio spatial cues. Connectivity and Power This Philips HTS3532BL/94 5.1 Home Theatre System has one HDMI output that ensures that, regardless of what quality the media that you play is of, the picture is always perfect. You can also play media directly from a USB on the system which has one composite video output and one Aux input as well. It also has one FM antenna with 40 presets to brighten up your busy mornings. This system also has Music iLink, digital optical input, speaker jacks which fit easily. Apple fans need not despair, you can listen to your favorite playlists from your iPod and iPhone which can be connected to the system as well. This system from Philips needs 220 - 240 V and 50 Hz of power to function. It consumes 55 W of power when it is in use and 0.9 W when in standby mode.

At 31 grams light and 5.4 mm thin, iPod nano is designed to provide hours of entertainment with maximum portability. The 2.5‑inch Multi‑Touch display lets you see more of the music, photos and videos you love. Buttons let you quickly play, pause and change songs, or adjust the volume. The smooth anodised aluminium design makes iPod nano feel as good as it sounds. And it wouldn’t be iPod nano without a gorgeous selection of colours. Watch episodes of your favourite TV programmes, Hollywood blockbusters, free video podcasts and home videos on your iPod nano. View them on the widescreen 2.5‑inch Multi‑Touch display. Tap to play, fast‑forward, rewind and pause. With iPod nano, you can have a little entertainment whenever — and wherever — you want. Pairing iPod nano with Bluetooth-enabled headphones and supported speakers is a cinch. And if your car’s sound system is Bluetooth enabled, when you sit down in the driver’s seat, your iPod nano is ready to pick up where you left off. Without missing a beat. FM radio keeps you up on what’s going on out there — the game, the top news stories, your favourite talk shows — whatever you love listening to. Just flick the radio dial to change stations and tap to set your favourites. And with Live Pause, you won’t miss a minute. iPod nano is the perfect workout partner. Since Nike+ support and a pedometer are built into iPod nano, you can easily track your steps, distance, pace, time and calories burned. Built‑in Bluetooth technology also lets you wirelessly connect to heart rate monitors and headphones, making it easier to exercise. Chances are, there’s an audio or video podcast for just about anything you’re into. And you can listen to and watch it right on iPod nano. Browse podcasts through the podcast directory in iTunes. When you find one (or more than one) you’re interested in, subscribe. That way, you won’t miss an episode. And the best part? Thousands of them are free. iPod nano comes with accessibility features that help people with disabilities enjoy music, audiobooks and more

productBaseInfoV1.title: VEEYES VS-510 Voltage Stabilizer for Air conditioners upto 2 TN (Working Range : 180V - 270V)(Off White)
productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: Features: Intelligent Time Delay Low/High Voltage Cut Off 4 KVA - Upto 1.5 Tn Airconditioner Working Range 150 to 270V Instant Start Why it is important ? Since you are spending a lot of money when you purchase TVs, Home Theatre, ACs, Refrigerator, Deep Freezer and so on. And, it is very important to take care of them for longer life. The best way to do this would be with this It comes equipped with features, such as an Elegantly-designed Cabinet with a Wallmounting Facility and Built-in Thermal Overload Protection to efficiently protect your devices in voltage-fluctuating conditions, while making sure that your devices and your home look appealing. LED Status Indication: This voltage stabiliser comes with a user-friendly LED Status Indication feature to showcase the input and output performance. Thus, when the device is powered up, the Input LED light glows, and the Output LED light indicates the mode of operation. Wide Input Range: This voltage stabilizer is equipped to handle a wide range of input voltage to keep your devices functional even at low voltage levels, so that you can enjoy uninterrupted entertainment, cooling, etc., no matter how low, high, or unpredictable the input voltage range is. Time Delay Systems When power comes or you switch on your stabilizer, the stabilizer energizes immediately but gives it's output to power appliance after some delay. This feature enables a time lapse so that the inbuilt compressor (in case of a refrigerator or air conditioner etc.) gets sufficient time to balance the current flow, when a short duration power cut occurs. Overload Protection The overload protection helps to turns off the stabilizer output completely in case of short circuit or any kind of burn-out due to overload occurs.
